FT  28 APR 94 / UK Company News: Kleinwort Benson 'very active'
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Shares of Kleinwort Benson, the investment banking and management business
concern, rose 38p to 483p yesterday as Lord Rockley, chairman, told the
