<HEADLINE>
FT  28 APR 94 / People: Wardle Storey
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Alan Mackinnon, formerly marketing director of Wardle Storey, has been
appointed vice-president, sales and marketing Europe, for GUILFORD Europe.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Guilford Europe.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P2258 Lace and Warp Knit Fabric Mills.
