FT  28 APR 94 / Hutchison issues Orange tariffs
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Hutchison Microtel yesterday announced five price plans for its Orange
mobile telephone network, which is launched today.
There are to be no monthly charges. Its plan for occasional users costs
Pounds 15 a month including 15 minutes of airtime. Orange to Orange calls
after that cost 12.5p. Heavy users can have 540 minutes of airtime a month
for Pounds 100, after which calls cost 7p a minute.
Hutchison's Orange, Page 31
